boat.full_description:
Moonshadow was built in 1985 in Emsworth by E Dridge designed by John Sharp. A traditional ketch along the lines of a long Falmouth quay punt she has been cruised in the Mediteranean for a number of years. 

A 40 hp yanmar diesle engine fitted in 2009.
